title: Tipicos & Pupusas
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Honduran food at a restaurant directly across from the main park/square. All dishes come with complimentary repollo (cabbage salad) and ensalada (mix of vegetables, peppers, spices), which are both vegan. Frijoles pupusas are vegan. Many dishes can be made vegan - ask.
streetAddress: Calla de La Plaza, Across from Parque Central
